Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要开开关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕有什么变化？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有显示了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D14在闪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边的屏幕如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M15在亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒GUNDAM吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fs60\pos(512,550)\1c&H00d9ebea}口袋里的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需工具、渣古的部件及武器，这三样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工具买就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部件呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆的残骸在这卫星殖民地到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里找能用的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有被联邦捉到的危险的呦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到存放武器的地方去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装有武器的货柜车还剩两台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米舍遗留的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被联邦士兵拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩有一台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在停车场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个货柜车已停了三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想查就请便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！不要留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是寄放的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道，知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号码是租用车的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查查停车时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，我有好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前就停在这没动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！看看里面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军从这个卫星殖民地滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩，你做什么？住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！喂！住手，住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还我爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们杀了我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为联邦军在这里建造基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了战争，爸爸他……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还我爸爸……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，你的心情我是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这是吉翁军不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以以后不要再做这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把电磁斧，爆裂炮12发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大收获！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好，亚尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要扔了这辆货柜车，还得去弄一台新车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特别的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在还没接近GUNDAM之前就会被打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能偷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有点困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么好主意就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到好主意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲给我听听！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没杀他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏过去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这些发烟筒及气球去设陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点就选靠近联邦基地的森林较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那就不用担心会使人卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，接下来要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把GUNDAM引来，施以突击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话用电磁斧也能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易的吧，这下……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭丧着脸嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你爸爸不是要回来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不能跟你一起作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有要帮忙的事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战的事我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明天的任务是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能将这个包裹送一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送到那里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁盘里面有指示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果作战失败，我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了那个磁盘，照我的命令行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的工作，拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼死了之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是万一之时的防备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不会使用到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天2点，打倒GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成功地保护这卫星殖民地的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过个好圣诞节啊，亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼不会死吧！会赢吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的，交给我了，好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，巴尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊！请实现我的愿望！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓决不再捣蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的，我发誓！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不再在街上玩，直接回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不再把蛇或蜥蜴放在女生桌内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，所以，请你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你保佑巴尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解救这卫星殖民地以及大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿门！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是出击的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！亚尔，妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，让你们久等不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离船很近的地方，发生战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过窗户看到吉翁的船被击沈的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这也差一点就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向联邦军投降的吉翁舰里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然好像装有核子武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然载有核子武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照联邦的调查原是想基亚的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又会到这中立的殖民地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔怎么了？亚尔不是在这下车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要再打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要阻止巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渣古，接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三分钟后就和本基地接触
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“艾里克斯”的弹药余量状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手还剩五百发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究所来电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝支持行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克其中尉，出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，不追来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两台都往夏贝区了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克其中尉，撤回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在原地作战比较有利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏贝区是无人地区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林和它作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉！撤回！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用再战了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克其中尉怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着，只是昏过去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在渣古的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被轰得乱七八糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比绞肉还惨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，不要紧吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！要不要紧啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担架，快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不要紧吧！喂！孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点，喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，听好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个包裹里有我录的证言录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有证据文件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何这个卫星殖民地会成为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核子飞弹的目标？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽我所知的都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一我死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个交给警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大人们相信这是真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个卫星殖民地我想就会得救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想直接去警察局去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢？那样做……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿不作战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像自己会变得不像自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是恨联邦，也不是要替队长他们的报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法表达的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和它，想跟GUNDAM它打一仗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我是士兵的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由连我自己也不很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，我大概会死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为此事憎恨联邦士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或GUNDAM的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也只是和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是做他们认为该做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要怨恨他人或责怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我最后的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果运气好活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且战争结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回到这卫星殖民地的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了！亚尔，健康的生活啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向克莉斯问好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，亚尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才在喊叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八点半左右
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是好天气啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像神在庆祝新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，我找不到毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也真是的，你想把厨房弄得到处是水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！借用一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子的爹，等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真是没办法！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔差不多该出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕带了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成大人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比较稳重了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要转任到地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟你道别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然的消息，吓到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原想和巴尼打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能由亚尔转达一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说：“多谢他对我的关照！”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想，巴尼也一定会觉得很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，亚尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见！克莉斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫长痛苦的战争终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平日子到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这卫星殖民地里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争也留下了很深的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是只是失去了校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也失去了许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母，兄弟以及友人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和平是由许多人的牺性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所换来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们不要忘记这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你们长大成人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，哪里在痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再掀起这样的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界的和平，希望你们能努力奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫老师等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们活下来的人所承担的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争马上会再开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定是更、更夸张的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又好玩又大的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对嘛，然后不只是弹壳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以捡实弹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许还能捡到军队的枪呢！

