Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:07:01.64,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊！让我来爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:15.66,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抬头望天空虽遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:22.37,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但有无尽的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:33.37,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是的  从被创造的世界里  逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:38.48,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想成为自由之身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:44.99,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直不断奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:51.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能来到天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:56.11,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我将化为一阵风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:08:02.04,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我相信会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:07.64,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我永不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:16.95,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每个人都说如此就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:24.57,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然沉默不语
